 1316   static const mxArray *emlrt_marshallOut(const char * u)
 1317   {
 1318     const mxArray *y;
 1319     const mxArray *m0;
 1320     y = NULL;
 1321     m0 = emlrtCreateString(u);
 1322     emlrtAssign(&y, m0);
 1323     return y;
 1324   }
 1325   
 1326   static const mxArray *b_emlrt_marshallOut(const uint32_T u)
 1327   {
 1328     const mxArray *y;
 1329     const mxArray *m1;
 1330     y = NULL;
 1331     m1 = emlrtCreateNumericMatrix(1, 1, mxUINT32_CLASS, mxREAL);
 1332     *(uint32_T *)mxGetData(m1) = u;
 1333     emlrtAssign(&y, m1);
 1334     return y;
 1335   }
